Did you know that 1 out of 2 people think that women are sometimes responsible for situations of sexual harassment in public spaces due to their attitudes or appearance? This is the result of a recent L’Oréal Paris study conducted with Ipsos in 20 countries*.

It’s time to shift the mindset on sexual harassment in public places. Join @lorealparis and @righttobeorg in the fight against street harassment.

Take the Stand Up training and learn how to react when facing it. 
To get trained in 10 minutes, check the link in bio.
